* Quality of service in computer network trafficking refers to resource
  reservation control mechanisms
* Quantum of Solace, works related to Ian Fleming's James Bond: ** The
  original short story ** A 2008 cinematic production with a plot written by
  Michael G. Wilson
* Quarterdeck Office Systems, a software company that is now part of Symantec
* Queen of the South F.C., a professional association football club formed and
  in existence since 1919 in Dumfries, Scotland, often colloquially abbreviated
  to QoS (as listed on the club badge)
* Queensland Ornithological Society, a state birding organisation in Australia
